==Summary==

This DIP draft mirrors the BIP-format PQC commitment draft and documents
Dogecoin-specific interoperability requirements:

* Tagged OP_RETURN commitment scripts only:
** <code>6a24 464c4331 <32 bytes></code> (Falcon-512 / <code>FLC1</code>)
** <code>6a24 44494c32 <32 bytes></code> (Dilithium2 / <code>DIL2</code>)
* Commitment value:
** <code>SHA256(pubkey || signature)</code>

==Non-goals==

This draft does not yet define consensus opcode changes. It only standardizes
commitment script shape and hashing convention for tool-level compatibility.
